import math
s=float(input("Enter the opposite side of a triangle"))
p=float(input("Enter the adjacent side of a triangle"))
hyp=math.sqrt(s**2+p**2)
print("other side of the triangle is {} whose opposite side is{} and adjacent is{}".format(hyp,s,p))
OUTPUT:
Enter the opposite side of a triangle3
Enter the adjacent side of a triangle4
other side of the triangle is 5.0 whose opposite side is3.0 and adjacent is4.0
